'''北卡罗来纳州议会大厦'''是[[美国|美国]][[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]政府的主要建筑，设有北卡罗莱纳州州长办公室，位于州首府[[罗利_(北卡罗来纳州)|罗利]]的联合广场，东伊登顿街1号，希腊复兴建筑。1833年7月4日，西蒙斯·琼斯·贝克为其奠基举行了[[共济会|共济会]]仪式<ref>{{cite book | last = Smith | first = Claiborne T., Jr. | editor = Powell, William S. | title = Dictionary of North Carolina Biography | volume = 1. (A-C) | year = 1979 | publisher = [[University_of_North_Carolina_Press|University of North Carolina Press]] | location = [[Chapel_Hill,_North_Carolina|Chapel Hill, North Carolina]], USA | isbn = 0-8078-1329-X | pages = 92–93 }}</ref>。1840年完工<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nchistoricsites.org/capitol/default.htm | title = North Carolina Historic Sites: State Capitol | date = 2010-06-14 | publisher = North Carolina Historic Sites, a division of the North Carolina Department of Cultural Resources | location = Raleigh, North Carolina | accessdate = 2/4/2011 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130607155823/http://www.nchistoricsites.org/capitol/default.htm | archive-date = 2013-06-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。主要由Ithiel Town建筑公司和亚历山大·杰克逊·戴维斯设计<ref name="ncarchitects">{{cite web |url=http://ncarchitects.lib.ncsu.edu/people/P000026 |title=Nichols, William (1780-1853) |work=North Carolina Architects and Builders: A Biographical Directory |publisher=The NCSU Libraries Digital Scholarship and Publishing Center |accessdate=2009-11-29 |archive-date=2010-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609051026/http://ncarchitects.lib.ncsu.edu/people/P000026 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

北卡罗来纳州议会大厦在1973年被宣布为[[国家历史地标|国家历史地标]]<ref name="nhlsum"/><ref name="nrhpinv2">{{Cite journal|title={{PDFlink|[http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/70000476.pdf National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: Capitol]|32 KB}}|date=April 22, 1970 |author=Jack Zehmer and Sherry Ingram |publisher=National Park Service}} and {{PDFlink|[http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/70000476.pdf ''Accompanying five photos, exterior and interior, from c. 1940 and 1969'']|32 KB}}</ref>

